,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"通天閣係咪好商業化唔抵去?"},{"pid":"68c84e26d6673909c08b3c334465651df5a40109","tid":155122,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議留1、2日去京都<br />\n嵐山&amp;鞍馬真係靚到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以試埋流水麵&amp;川床料理<br />\n食既話平安神宮附近個小寶蛋包飯平又正<br />\n京都車站個東洋亭都好春正<br />\n但果邊真係冇乜地方啱香港遊客shopping,<br />\n有時間可以去錦市場同高木批發超市睇睇</blockquote><br />\n巴打黎緊都諗住去嵐山，但係我個fd話好伏，特別係竹林個到，我5月尾去會唔會無野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad989a01341ac0cb3e97cb33cd34178dae6a8026","tid":155122,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"第一次去一定要去黑門市場<br />\n但淨係去專食toro o個間鋪頭食toro好na~"},{"pid":"4a290454b75ace8f60d060934b6c54342b49c03f","tid":155122,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未去過黑門可以去睇下既<br />\n成條街都廣東話啫<br />\n出黎可以落日本橋J acg 野<br />\n中間又有千日前道具街<br />\n落到底又去到通天閣, 值得一上的<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以帶埋囡囡走飛田新地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食野咪食下d 關西風味囉<br />\n以前去道頓掘有檔八爪魚丸好鬼正, 出名大粒<br />\n樓上就有大阪燒鋪<br />\n拉麵就千其唔好去金龍<br />\n<br />\n有興趣食蟹可以J 蟹道樂, 坐和式個隻體驗先會特別d 咁</blockquote><br />\n咩係飛田新地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想瘋狂食！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飛田新地都係食野既地方<br />\n不過係食囡囡<br />\n入面D女係好高質"},{"pid":"408bfd2613189ab7cd6141d2221e9e71ccf84588","tid":155122,"uid":39120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T06:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>建議留1、2日去京都<br />\n嵐山&amp;鞍馬真係靚到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以試埋流水麵&amp;川床料理<br />\n食既話平安神宮附近個小寶蛋包飯平又正<br />\n京都車站個東洋亭都好春正<br />\n但果邊真係冇乜地方啱香港遊客shopping,<br />\n有時間可以去錦市場同高木批發超市睇睇</blockquote><br />\n巴打黎緊都諗住去嵐山，但係我個fd話好伏，特別係竹林個到，我5月尾去會唔會無野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔係紅葉期<br />\n嵐山其實一般<br />\n唔算話好靚<br />\n但幾舒服既<br />\n有時間可以去<br />\n無時間skip左唔可惜"},{"pid":"92bb72241bb1c4d8b56f3e584961b0b11a44dbd3","tid":155122,"uid":82456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"巴打買左USJ門票同快證未?  依家去有Universal Cool japan 玩！一定要去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007b1a5b852447ed02faad5de21b656739878391","tid":155122,"uid":12482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"如果去天王寺動物園個頭 千其唔好入去附近啲夾錢公仔舖 伏到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係想夾公仔扭蛋 去日本橋就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a5e5222167581658f9413c63d10cc0bdbce91c","tid":155122,"uid":20208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次去一定要去黑門市場<br />\n但淨係去專食toro o個間鋪頭食toro好na~</blockquote><br />\n有無名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66073111c888a59838252bad607666e07ca2c11e","tid":155122,"uid":7070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一次去一定要去黑門市場<br />\n但淨係去專食toro o個間鋪頭食toro好na~</blockquote><br />\n有無名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但有好多人話黑門市場唔值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}